{"tid":2462933,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"5歲女童虐殺案 繼母曾向丈夫表示「睇佢前面就憎佢後面」","createTime":"2021-03-26T10:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T10:43:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c1a11cd6646a2d53e42839b25edba659476757","tid":2462933,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"5歲女童疑遭生父及繼母虐待致死案，今於高等法院續審，繼母繼續自辯。控方盤問時指，繼母曾於微信向丈夫形容「睇佢（女童）前面就憎佢後面」，繼母今解釋只是抒發情緒，因面對女童覺得壓力很大。控方續指，兩童曾表示想搬回舊居，但繼母漠視他們意願，繼母今承認兩童的確不願意跟自己回家，男童稱欲回祖母家，女童則指「夜晚想去McDonald瞓」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210326/OQGXVKS3HZHCPOKILQU5DECZ5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210326%2FOQGXVKS3HZHCPOKILQU5DECZ5Y%2F&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Gqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=28152464\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210326%2FOQGXVKS3HZHCPOKILQU5DECZ5Y%2F&h=7d83a242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210326/OQGXVKS3HZHCPOKILQU5DECZ5Y/</a>"},{"pid":"022f9a8c5d127dbf5e05f6d3bd7cb1fa3ca59088","tid":2462933,"uid":272343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1c1a11cd6646a2d53e42839b25edba659476757","tid":2462933,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"5歲女童疑遭生父及繼母虐待致死案，今於高等法院續審，繼母繼續自辯。控方盤問時指，繼母曾於微信向丈夫形容「睇佢（女童）前面就憎佢後面」，繼母今解釋只是抒發情緒，因面對女童覺得壓力很大。控方續指，兩童曾表示想搬回舊居，但繼母漠視他們意願，繼母今承認兩童的確不願意跟自己回家，男童稱欲回祖母家，女童則指「夜晚想去McDonald瞓」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210326/OQGXVKS3HZHCPOKILQU5DECZ5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210326%2FOQGXVKS3HZHCPOKILQU5DECZ5Y%2F&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Gqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=28152464\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210326%2FOQGXVKS3HZHCPOKILQU5DECZ5Y%2F&h=7d83a242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210326